Package com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateMoodActivity
    CreateMoodActivity will be similar to the EditMoodActivity in such a way that the format will be the same.
    EditMoodActivity
    The EditMoodActivity pulls any current details about a certain mood event and presents them to the participant.
    FilterMapActivity
    FilterMapActivity sets up the map view that displays the mood events that have gone under filtering requirements prior to being displayed.
    FollowersActivity
    FollowersActivity displays a list view of all of the participants that are following you.
    FollowingActivity
    The FollowingActivity allows a function where you would be able to search for other users of the app (exact name).
    FollowingMapActivity
    FollowingMapActivity allows you to view a map of mood events of your following participants.
    FollowRequestActivity
    FollowRequestActivity displays the pending requests of anyone who wishes to follow your mood events.
    LoginActivity
    LoginActivity is the login page of the app, and the first activity that will run upon opening the app.
    MyFeedActivity
    MyFeedActivity contains the functionality of filtering with your mood following list.
    MyProfileActivity  
    RecentMapActivity
    RecentMapActivity displays the recent mood events around you (5 km).
    SearchActivity  
    ViewMoodEventActivity
    ViewMoodEventActivity is called upon a clicked mood event on some list view.
